msgstr "根据提供的草稿上下文建议匹配的已有分类和标签。"

msgid "Find terms"
msgstr "查找分类标签"

msgid "Use Cloud-managed Site Knowledge to find related public content for operator-reviewed links."
msgstr "使用 Cloud 托管站点知识查找相关公开内容，供运营者审阅链接。"

msgid "Find links"
msgstr "查找链接"

msgid "Image Candidates"
msgstr "图片候选"

msgid "Find image-source candidates for featured or inline use. Import still requires a governed handoff."
msgstr "查找用于特色图或正文图片的图片来源候选。导入仍需要治理交接。"

msgid "Find images"
msgstr "查找图片"

msgid "Fallback Bundles"
msgstr "降级包"

msgid "Article Planning Bundle"
msgstr "文章规划包"

msgid "Build one combined research, image, knowledge, outline, and handoff bundle when an operator needs a compact fallback package."
msgstr "当运营者需要精简降级包时，生成一个包含研究、图片、知识、大纲和交接内容的组合包。"

msgid "Article topic"
msgstr "文章主题"

msgid "Build bundle"
msgstr "生成包"

